You are here:

Configure the table widget properties to expose the bulk action defined in the Visualforce page.

Open the CRM Analytics dashboard that contains the table widget.
Edit the dashboard.
Select the table widget.
In the widget properties, select Show custom action.
Enter the following widget properties.
PROPERTY    DESCRIPTION
Custom Action Label  Label for the action in the action menu.
Visualforce Page Name  API name of the Visualforce page.
Visualforce Namespace Prefix  Optional. Namespace prefix specified for the Visualforce page.
Save the dashboard.

Create a Visualforce Page That Executes the Action
title: Assigning Bulk Actions to Table Widgets in Salesforce Analytics
